title: Kafe anno 1762
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Buffet, European, German, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A nice cafe in a very old house with outdoor seating in a garden. Also has a small shop and a German sourdough bread bakery. Everything is organic and a lot is local food. On Sundays the brunch buffet serves mainly vegetarian food, some of which may be vegan; please inquire. The week's soup with salad and bread is always vegetarian, of which at times may be vegan; please inquire. Will prepare vegan meals on request.
